description:
This is a 12 minute workout called '10 Minute Morning Breathwork Routine I The Key To Happiness' from the channel Breathe With Sandy.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Start your mornings with a calm breathing technique to invite some positivity and joy into your day. By using the breath, mixing conscious breathing with conscious thinking, we can influence our day, and our life to go in any direction that we would like.
